            <div id="secondarynews" class="module">
              <h3>
                <a href="http://www.futurelab.org.uk/projects/games-in-education">Serious Games</a>
              </h3>
              <p>
                <a href="http://www.futurelab.org.uk/projects/games-in-education">
                  <img height="77" width="77" src="/resources/images/games.jpg" alt="Games" />
                </a>
              </p>
              <p>Our latest <a href="http://www.futurelab.org.uk/projects/games-in-education" title="Literature review">literature review</a> looks at the challenges of embedding serious games in education and methods for assessing games for teaching.</p>
              <h3>
                <a href="http://dreamjobs.infocow.org.uk">Dream Jobs Competition</a>
              </h3>
              <p>
                <a href="http://dreamjobs.infocow.org.uk">
                  <img height="77" width="77" src="/resources/images/infocow-77.jpg" alt="Dream Jobs Competition" />
                </a>
              </p>
              <p><a href="http://dreamjobs.infocow.org.uk" title="Dream Jobs competition">Infocow</a> and icould have joined forces to offer 14-19 year-olds the chance to spend a day with one of six people at the top of their game. Find out how you could win the chance to be a racing car designer for the day...</p>
